Invocation Name: winging it cafe
des: This skill parses the public Facebook page for Wingin' It Cafe in Redmond, WA and tells the user what the special of the day or the burger for any specified day is. Wingin' It is open Monday to Friday, so requests for the special on weekends will result in being given information for the following Monday.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
